Enum ContractualSupplementEnum

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ContractualSupplementEnum>

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ContractualSupplementEnum>
    public enum ContractualSupplementEnum
extends java.lang.Enum<ContractualSupplementEnum>
    The enumerated values to define the supplements to a base set of ISDA Definitions that are applicable to the transaction.
